Fliq/Brix

"Okay, we've got all the comp boards out." said Brix, "Let's go load 
them up in the shuttle."

Brix and Fliq pick up an arm load of equipement and head off towards 
the shuttle.
______________________________________________________________________
Savage

Savage watches the bot travel across trees and land with a thud. He 
can't tell if he's dead or not. But even if he isn't dead, that bot 
will never be the same. It's time to get some rest and make scars.

Savage uses the rest of it's power to start flying towards it's cave.
______________________________________________________________________
Zava

Zava catches up with The Chosne Ones. She nearly screams.

"Oh My God! It's the Chosen Ones!"

Zava runs up and hugs Deemos. Than she explains herself.

"Deemos! Hi, my name is Zava, and I've been watching your work from 
Cybertron. I love the destruction you've been causing. Please, let me 
join you!"
______________________________________________________________________
Gotron

Gotron arrives at The Alliance Base, watching two bots enter it. He 
immediatly recognizes one: Zardus! The leader of the alliance, the 
man he has admired for years. Gotron runs up to him before the doors 
can close.

"Zardus, wait! My name is Gotron, and I would like to join the 
Alliance!"
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream sets up a little shooting range in the Pred cave and 
begins to practice firing.
______________________________________________________________________
Vulois

Vulois finishes taking the computers apart. All that remains is some 
other mechanical devices. Vulois begins to think about the limits 
he's put on Child, whether they were right or not. He finaly decideds 
that the Child is too important to be left open. He begins removing 
the other pieces.

(So much for the ever kind Matrix Emmisarry Vulois, eh? What a jerk!)
